23|82|They said, ‘What, when we are dead and become dust and bones, shall we be resurrected?
23|83|Certainly, we and our fathers were promised this before. [But] these are nothing but myths of the ancients.’
23|84|Say, ‘To whom does the earth belong and whoever it contains, if you know?’
