29|9|Those who have faith and do righteous deeds, We will surely admit them among the righteous.
29|10|Among the people there are those who say, ‘We have faith in Allah,’ but if such a one is tormented in Allah’s cause, he takes persecution by the people for Allah’s punishment. Yet if there comes any help from your Lord, they will say, ‘We were indeed with you.’ Does not Allah know best what is in the breasts of the creatures?
29|11|Allah shall surely ascertain those who have faith, and He shall surely ascertain the hypocrites.
29|12|The faithless say to the faithful, ‘Follow our way and we will bear [responsibility for] your iniquities.’ They will not bear anything of their iniquities. They are indeed liars.
